  "title": "showParentLevel not working when preceded by breadcrumb widget",
  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nWhen a hierarchicalMenu widget and a breadcrumb widget are used, using the same attributes, then the showParentLevel false doesn't work, stays default true.\r\n\r\nIf you remove the breadcrumb widget, the showParentLevel false works again.\r\n\r\nExpected to also hide the parents when the option is set to false",
